   "cell_type": "raw",
   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Semantic Router Project\\n\",\"**NLP Project 99 of 100** — Route user questions to specialized NLP pipelines based on semantic intent.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Learning Objectives\\n\",\"1. Build an intent-based routing system using embeddings.\\n\",\"2. Route to different handlers (QA, summarization, translation, etc.).\\n\",\"3. Handle fallback for unrecognized intents.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import subprocess, sys, importlib\\nfor pkg in ['pandas','numpy','scikit-learn','sentence-transformers']:\\n    try: importlib.import_module(pkg.replace('-','_'))\\n    except ImportError: subprocess.check_call([sys.executable,'-m','pip','install','-q',pkg])\\nprint('Ready.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd\\nfrom sklearn.metrics.pairwise import cosine_similarity\\nfrom sentence_transformers import SentenceTransformer\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nSEED = 42; np.random.seed(SEED)\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Define Routes\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"ROUTES = {\\n    'qa': ['What is machine learning?','How does Python work?','Explain neural networks','What are embeddings?'],\\n    'summarize': ['Summarize this article','Give me a summary','TLDR of this document','Condense this text'],\\n    'translate': ['Translate this to French','Convert to Spanish','Say this in German','How do you say hello in Japanese?'],\\n    'code': ['Write Python code for','Generate a function that','Create a script to','Code this algorithm'],\\n    'sentiment': ['What is the sentiment?','Is this positive or negative?','Analyze the tone','How does this text feel?'],\\n}\\n\\n# Encode route examples\\nmodel = SentenceTransformer('all-MiniLM-L6-v2')\\nroute_embeddings = {}\\nfor route, examples in ROUTES.items():\\n    route_embeddings[route] = model.encode(examples)\\nprint(f'Routes: {list(ROUTES.keys())}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Router Implementation\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"def route_query(query, threshold=0.4):\\n    query_emb = model.encode([query])\\n    best_route, best_score = 'fallback', 0.0\\n    for route, embs in route_embeddings.items():\\n        sims = cosine_similarity(query_emb, embs)[0]\\n        max_sim = sims.max()\\n        if max_sim > best_score:\\n            best_score = max_sim\\n            best_route = route if max_sim > threshold else 'fallback'\\n    return best_route, round(best_score, 3)\\n\\n# Test queries\\ntest_queries = [\\n    'What is deep learning?', 'Summarize the document for me', 'Translate hello to Spanish',\\n    'Write a sorting function in Python', 'Is this review positive?',\\n    'What is the weather today?', 'How tall is the Eiffel Tower?',\\n    'Give me the key points of this article', 'Convert to Japanese please',\\n]\\n\\nfor q in test_queries:\\n    route, score = route_query(q)\\n    print(f'  [{route:10s}] (sim={score}) {q}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Evaluation\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"test_set = [\\n    ('What is NLP?', 'qa'), ('Summarize this paragraph', 'summarize'),\\n    ('Translate to French', 'translate'), ('Code a web scraper', 'code'),\\n    ('Is this comment toxic?', 'sentiment'),\\n]\\n\\ncorrect = sum(1 for q, expected in test_set if route_query(q)[0] == expected)\\nprint(f'Routing accuracy: {correct}/{len(test_set)} = {correct/len(test_set):.0%}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Semantic routing uses embedding similarity** to match queries to handlers.\\n\",\"- **Few-shot examples per route are sufficient** for decent routing accuracy.\\n\",\"- **Fallback handling is critical** for queries outside defined routes.\\n\",\"- **For production, use semantic-router library** or fine-tune on real query logs.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
